            </li>
            <li>
              
                <p>
Block \(M_{1}\) is moving downward
</p>
              
              <optioninput location="random" name="foil6" options="('True','False')" correct="False">
</optioninput>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </optionresponse>
      </part>
      <part loncapaid="23">
        
          <p>
Part 4. 
During the motion of the blocks, the magnitude of the force of tension acting on each block is the same at all times, as long as:
</p>
        
        <optionresponse texlayout="horizontal" max="10" randomize="no" loncapaid="27">
          <ul>
